Author: lostmyshitinamuseum
Text: I’ve recovered several times and this point, and I’ve also noticed that every time I recover, it’s different. Some things are easier than last time, other things are more difficult. But it kinda makes sense - I’m different from who I was when I was fifteen, so of course it will be a different experience when I’m 20

Author: tigerchik
Text: agree, everyone's brain is different! Glad you are liking how you look!
